MERUBAH ALIAS PHPMYADMIN DI LARAGON
=======
PATH	: LARAGON > ETC > APACHE2 > ALIAS > PHPMYADMIN
* LINE 1
* Alias /NAMA_ALIASNYA_DISINI "C:/laragon/etc/apps/phpMyAdmin/"



MEMBUKA REMOTE MYSQL DI LARAGON
=====
PATH	: LARAGON > ETC > APACHE2 > ALIAS > PHPMYADMIN
* UBAH REQUIRE LOCAL (ATAU SEBAGAINYA)
* MENJADI REQUIRE ALL GRANTED

<Directory "C:/laragon/etc/apps/phpMyAdmin/">
	Options Indexes FollowSymLinks MultiViews
	AllowOverride all  
 
	Require all granted
</Directory>

* JANGAN LUPA MEMBUKA PORT MELALUI FIREWALL
